title: Rysons16 Soap Filled Scourer Pads, Heavy Duty, 16 Pack
features: Multipurpose: These 16 soap-filled scourer pads are ideal for tackling tough, baked-on messes on various surfaces.
Dual-Action Cleaning: The abrasive scourer side removes stubborn stains, while the soap-infused side cuts through grease and grime.
Heavy-Duty: Designed for the toughest cleaning jobs, these pads are durable and long-lasting.
Convenient Pack: This pack contains 16 pads, ensuring you have a sufficient supply for all your cleaning needs.
Versatile Usage: Suitable for use on pots, pans, sinks, countertops, and other kitchen surfaces.
description: Tackle tough cleaning jobs with ease using these heavy-duty soap-filled scourer pads. These 16 pads are designed to cut through grime, grease, and baked-on messes, leaving surfaces sparkling clean. The rough and durable texture provides excellent scrubbing power, while the soap infusion helps break down stubborn stains. Suitable for various surfaces, including pots, pans, sinks, and countertops. These versatile scourer pads are a must-have for any household, offering reliable cleaning performance for the toughest tasks. Measuring approximately 6 cm x 9 cm, they provide ample surface area for efficient cleaning. Bring home this convenient pack and enjoy effortless cleaning.
